# qbittorrent magnet

* https://www.linuxquestions.org/questions/linux-newbie-8/how-to-add-magnet-support-to-firefox-460090/

* http://kb.mozillazine.org/Register_protocol

* /usr/share/applications/qbittorrent.desktop: 
~~~
[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Encoding=UTF-8
Name=qBitorrent
Comment=A BitTorrent client in Qt
Icon=/path/to/icon.xpm
Exec=/path/to/application/executable
Terminal=false
Categories=Tags;Describing;Application
MimeType=application/x-bittorrent;application/x-torrent;
~~~

* /usr/share/applications/defaults.list:
~~~
x-scheme-handler/magnet=qbittorrent.desktop
~~~
